Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.40,0:01:28.73,OP-CHI,,0,0,0,,快听
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.98,OP-CHI,,0,0,0,,世界仿佛伸着懒腰
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.40,OP-CHI,,0,0,0,,迈起了步子
